        "subject": "LU-744 llite: Change interface of ll_get_fsname",
        "message": "LU-744 llite: Change interface of ll_get_fsname\n\nAs of commit d8b486644ceef57c7388e8049b90bde4bf967500, the ll_sb_info\nstructure no longer has a pointer to the vfsmount structre. This change\nfixes up some incompatibilities between that patch these two:\n\n    Ibc077b46728a1358e51a345ec13c966fc947c428\n    I76c840aef5ca9a3a4619f06fcaee7de7f95b05f5\n\nby changing the interface to ll_get_fsname.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: Ie627ecedb33914897594ce99af0ef70654e351b1\n"
